text: Sanjula Sudhakar Naik (born 6 October 1996) is a Goan cricketer.Players She plays for Goa and made her debut in major domestic cricket on 6 December 2014 in a one-day match against Rajasthan.Goa vs Rajasthan She has played 16 List A and 19 Women's Twenty20 matches.statistics_lists == References == Category:Goa women cricketers Category:1996 births Category:Living people
